ry Kissinger">Kissinger</a> • <a href="/wiki/Cyrus_Vance" title="Cyrus Vance">Vance</a> • <a href="/wiki/Edmund_Muskie" title="Edmund Muskie">Muskie</a> • <a href="/wiki/Alexander_Haig" title="Alexander Haig">Haig</a> • <a href="/wiki/George_P._Shultz" title="George P. Shultz">Shultz</a> • <a href="/wiki/James_Baker" title="James Baker">Baker</a> • <a href="/wiki/Lawrence_Eagleburger" title="Lawrence Eagleburger">Eagleburger</a> • <a href="/wiki/Warren_Christopher" title="Warren Christopher">Christopher</a> • <a href="/wiki/Madeleine_Albright" title="Madeleine Albright">Albright</a> • <a href="/wiki/Colin_Powell" title="Colin Powell">Powell</a> • <strong class="selflink">Rice</strong> • <a href="/wiki/Hillary_Rodham_Clinton" title="Hillary Rodham Clinton">Clinton</a></div>
